  Text: "Say you'll stay\r\nDon't come and go, \nlike you do\r\nSway my way\r\nYeah,
    I need to know all about \nyou\r\nAnd there's no cure and no way to be sure\r\nWhy
    everything's turned \ninside \nout\r\nInstilling so much doubt\r\nIt makes me
    so tired, \nI feel so uninspired\r\nMy head is battling with my \nheart"
